The Model-Driven SAL (MD-SAL) is set of infrastructure services aimed at providing common and generic support to application and plugin developers.

The MD-SAL currently provides infrastructure services for:

* Data Store
* RPC / Service routing
* Notification subscription and publish services

This common model-driven infrastructure allows developers of applications and plugins to develop against one set of APIs derived from a single model: Java generated APIs, DOM APIs, and  REST APIs.


